#: ../../effects_and_compositions/transitions/composite.rst:17
msgid "Composite Transition"
msgstr "Transizione di composizione"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/transitions/composite.rst:19
msgid "Contents"
msgstr "Contenuti"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/transitions/composite.rst:21
msgid "The Composite transition combines the video data from two video tracks into one. This transition is used in combination with Alpha Channel information supplied by one of the :ref:`alpha_manipulation` or by the use of a :ref:`composite`. This Alpha Channel data describes how the data from the two video tracks should be combined. Until you define some alpha channel data using an :ref:`alpha_manipulation` or a Wipe File, changes in the Composite transition settings will have no visible effect."
msgstr ""
"La transizione di composizione combina i dati video di due tracce video in "
"una. Questa transizione viene utilizzata in combinazione con le informazioni "
"sul canale alfa fornite da uno dei :ref:`alpha_manipulation` o dall'uso di "
"un :ref:`composite`. Questi dati del canale alfa descrivono come combinare i "
"dati delle due tracce video. Finché non definisci alcuni dati del canale "
"alfa usando un :ref:`alpha_manipulation` o un Wipe File, le modifiche alle "
"impostazioni di transizione di composizione non avranno alcun effetto "
"visibile."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/transitions/composite.rst:23
msgid "Note: The disadvantages of the **Composite** transition are: luma bleed, and less precise position control. When compared to **Affine**, the **Composite** transition, it does not support rotation or skewing but it is much faster, albeit at the cost of luma bleed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/transitions/composite.rst:26
msgid "Alpha operations"
msgstr "Operazioni alfa"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/transitions/composite.rst:33
msgid "Alpha operation options are *Over*, *And*, *Or* and *Xor*:"
msgstr "Le opzioni di operazione alfa sono *Over*, *And*, *Or* e *Xor*:"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/transitions/composite.rst:35
msgid "Operation **Over**"
msgstr "Operazione *Over*"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/transitions/composite.rst:37
msgid "The clip with alpha information is located on the top track: the selected color acquires transparency."
msgstr ""
"La clip con le informazioni alfa si trova sulla traccia in alto: il colore "
"selezionato acquisisce trasparenza."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/transitions/composite.rst:38
msgid "The clip with alpha information is located on the bottom track: we see only the top clip."
msgstr ""
"La clip con le informazioni alfa si trova sulla traccia inferiore: vediamo "
"solo la clip superiore."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/transitions/composite.rst:44
msgid "Operation **And**"
msgstr "Operazione *And*"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/transitions/composite.rst:46
msgid "The clip with alpha information is located on the top track: the selected color becomes transparent."
msgstr ""
"La clip con le informazioni alfa si trova sulla traccia in alto: il colore "
"selezionato diventa trasparente."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/transitions/composite.rst:47
msgid "The clip with alpha information is located on the bottom track: everything in the image becomes transparent, except for the selected color."
msgstr ""
"La clip con le informazioni alfa si trova nella traccia inferiore: tutto "
"nell'immagine diventa trasparente, ad eccezione del colore selezionato."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/transitions/composite.rst:53
msgid "Operation **Or** clears any alpha information"
msgstr "L'operazione **Or** cancella tutte le informazioni alfa"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/transitions/composite.rst:59
msgid "Operation **Xor**"
msgstr "Operazione *Xor*"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/transitions/composite.rst:61
msgid "The clip with alpha information is located on the top track: everything in the image becomes transparent, except for the selected color."
msgstr ""
"La clip con le informazioni alfa si trova sulla traccia in alto: tutto "
"nell'immagine diventa trasparente, ad eccezione del colore selezionato."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/transitions/composite.rst:62
msgid "The clip with alpha information is located on the bottom track: the selected color acquires transparency."
msgstr ""
"La clip con le informazioni alfa si trova nella traccia inferiore: il colore "
"selezionato acquisisce trasparenza."

